name: BetaPro S&P/TSX 60 2x Daily Bull ETF
longDescription: CNDU seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the daily performance of the S and P/TSX 6 TM Index. CNDU does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
